FBIS3-44736 "drchi005_s_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-005 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Jan 1994 Northeast Asia Heilongjiang Discovers Counterfeit Banknotes SK0501042394 Harbin Heilongjiang People's Radio Network in Mandarin 1000 GMT 4 Jan 94 SK0501042394 Harbin Heilongjiang People's Radio Network Language: Mandarin Article Type:BFN [Text] A few days ago, Boli County public security organ cracked a serious case on using counterfeit banknotes. Criminal (Li Wengang) was arrested and put on record. On the evening of 29 December, Boli County public security bureau received a crime report that someone used counterfeit banknotes to buy gasoline and to pay for transportation fees. Trough investigation by inspectors, Criminal (Li Wengang) was captured in less than 10 hours. According to the confession, (Li Wengang) is a jobless person from Jixi city. He ganged up with two other persons to trade in counterfeit banknotes from Guangzhou and travelled to Boli County to purchase over 34,000 kg of soybeans, thus making more than 60,000 yuan counterfeit banknotes flow into society. At present, this case is undergoing further investigation.
